WEBVTT

0
00:00:00.439 --> 00:00:02.220
An understanding of different cultures

1
00:00:02.220 --> 00:00:04.260
is essential for effective communication.

2
00:00:05.019 --> 00:00:07.519
This skill known as cultural competency

3
00:00:07.659 --> 00:00:09.029
can be developed over time.

4
00:00:09.140 --> 00:00:11.399
It involves learning about other cultures

5
00:00:11.579 --> 00:00:13.640
and adapting communication styles

6
00:00:13.939 --> 00:00:17.350
to effectively interact with individuals from diverse backgrounds.

7
00:00:17.659 --> 00:00:19.479
The goal is to foster informed

8
00:00:19.579 --> 00:00:21.659
and effective cross cultural interactions.

9
00:00:22.700 --> 00:00:23.229
But

10
00:00:23.430 --> 00:00:24.350
it doesn't end there.

11
00:00:25.940 --> 00:00:28.920
While cultural competency provides a solid foundation,

12
00:00:29.180 --> 00:00:31.420
cultural humility is equally essential.

13
00:00:32.348 --> 00:00:33.490
Cultural humility

14
00:00:33.630 --> 00:00:37.340
emphasizes a lifelong process of self reflection and learning.

15
00:00:37.700 --> 00:00:39.950
Cultural humility also involves examining

16
00:00:39.950 --> 00:00:41.970
your own beliefs and cultural identities

17
00:00:42.110 --> 00:00:44.369
while respecting the perspectives of others,

18
00:00:44.669 --> 00:00:46.130
and both cultural competency

19
00:00:46.459 --> 00:00:49.610
and humility culminate in cultural responsiveness.

20
00:00:49.990 --> 00:00:53.770
Being culturally responsive involves understanding cultural differences

21
00:00:53.990 --> 00:00:56.840
and then adapting practices to be culturally appropriate

22
00:00:56.990 --> 00:01:00.849
and actively working to address systemic issues that contribute to disparities.

23
00:01:01.740 --> 00:01:05.559
It's essential to remember that cultural competency is just the beginning.

24
00:01:06.180 --> 00:01:09.610
By incorporating cultural humility and cultural responsiveness,

25
00:01:09.940 --> 00:01:13.059
we can create a more inclusive and effective healthcare environment.

26
00:01:13.900 --> 00:01:17.339
These 3 elements work together to ensure that all members feel valued,

27
00:01:17.620 --> 00:01:18.050
respected,

28
00:01:18.260 --> 00:01:20.180
and receive the highest quality of care.